rows.label: qst200715_msg0001
rows.name: It's no use... It's locked...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0004
rows.name: This is quite a complex mechanism...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0005
rows.name:
It will be impossible
for us to unlock it...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0006
rows.name:
Then I can't eat the
Mashimashidake-ppo?!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0007
rows.name: Leave it to Maumau-mau!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0008
rows.name: Can you do it?

rows.label: qst200715_msg0009
rows.name: Maffuffu...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0010
rows.name:
Maumau is a master phantom
thief... There has never been
a lock I couldn't pick-mau!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0011
rows.name: Let me see-mau.

rows.label: qst200715_msg0012
rows.name: Hmm, I see-mau...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0013
rows.name: Does it look like it'll open-ppo?

rows.label: qst200715_msg0014
rows.name: Wait a moment-mau...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0015
rows.name:
Come to think of it, this is
a collaborative effort, a
perfect division of labor-mau!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0016
rows.name:
Idaten fought the way here,
and Maumau will unlock the
treasure chest...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0017
rows.name:
It's a great treasure that we
could only obtain because our
two powers came together-mau.

rows.label: qst200715_msg0018
rows.name:
The two heroes, popular among Nopon and
children, joining hands and helping each
other... It's a truly exciting development-mau!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0019
rows.name:
More importantly, is the
Mashimashidake ready yet-ppo?

rows.label: qst200715_msg0020
rows.name: ...Guh. He's not listening at all-mau.

rows.label: qst200715_msg0021
rows.name:
This isn't new, is it? Idaten
and Maumau haven't been on the
same page from the start...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0022
rows.name:
That's true, but... Damn
it, to think this guy is
Maumau's rival-mau...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0023
rows.name:
Once we get the Mashimashidake, let's
hurry to Harapekko Canteen-ppo!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0024
rows.name:
I'll have them make a
delicious mushroom dish-ppo!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0025
rows.name: He really doesn't listen-mau...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0026
rows.name: Maumau, hurry and open it-ppo!!

rows.label: qst200715_msg0027
rows.name: Almost there-mau...

rows.label: qst200715_msg0028
rows.name:
Alright! The lock is off-mau! Now,
let's open the treasure chest-mau!
